source.name: President's Office--Juvenile Temporary Detention Center Cost Comparison
source.description: Comparing the per-day cost to host a juvenile detainee at the JTDC, to those of the Chicago Public Schools, and the Cook County Health and Hospitals System.  Average daily population of JTDC is 305 detainees.
